---
import TerminalLayout from '../layouts/TerminalLayout.astro';
---

<TerminalLayout>
  <div class="terminal-section">
    <h1 class="terminal-heading">HOW IT WORKS</h1>
    <p class="terminal-paragraph">Welcome to the Nosyt Labs terminal interface. This guide will help you navigate and utilize all features of this site.</p>
    
    <h2 class="terminal-subheading">NAVIGATION BASICS</h2>
    <div class="terminal-card">
      <div class="terminal-card-title">TERMINAL COMMANDS</div>
      <div class="terminal-card-content">
        <ul class="terminal-list">
          <li class="terminal-list-item">[TAB] - Return to main menu from any page</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">[H] - Access this help guide</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">[R] - Load project data</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">[1-5] - Quick navigation to main sections</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="terminal-subheading">SPECIAL FEATURES</h2>
    <div class="terminal-grid">
      <div class="terminal-card">
        <div class="terminal-card-title">DARK/LIGHT MODE</div>
        <div class="terminal-card-content">Toggle between terminal display modes using the power switch in the top-right corner.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-card">
        <div class="terminal-card-title">LAB ASSISTANT</div>
        <div class="terminal-card-content">Access your virtual pet by clicking [5] or typing "assistant" in the terminal. Feed, train, and send on missions.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-card">
        <div class="terminal-card-title">ACHIEVEMENTS</div>
        <div class="terminal-card-content">Unlock special achievements by exploring the site and interacting with different features.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-card">
        <div class="terminal-card-title">EASTER EGGS</div>
        <div class="terminal-card-content">Hidden features and jokes are scattered throughout the terminal. Try different commands to discover them.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="terminal-subheading">ADMIN PORTAL OVERVIEW</h2>
    <p class="terminal-paragraph">The Nosyt Labs site includes a comprehensive admin portal for site management (developer access only).</p>
    <div class="terminal-card">
      <div class="terminal-card-title">ADMIN CAPABILITIES</div>
      <div class="terminal-card-content">
        <ul class="terminal-list">
          <li class="terminal-list-item">Content Management System for updating projects and information</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">Analytics Dashboard for tracking site performance</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">Feature Toggle System for enabling/disabling site elements</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">Media Library for managing site assets</li>
          <li class="terminal-list-item">User Experience Controls for customizing animations and effects</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="terminal-paragraph">For site changes or updates, please contact the development team at support@nosytlabs.com.</p>
    
    <h2 class="terminal-subheading">COMMAND CHEATSHEET</h2>
    <div class="terminal-code">
      help           - Display this help guide<br>
      projects       - View all projects<br>
      about          - Company information<br>
      contact        - Contact information<br>
      assistant      - Access Lab Assistant<br>
      achievements   - View unlocked achievements<br>
      clear          - Clear terminal screen<br>
      version        - Display site version<br>
      easteregg      - Nice try, but that would be too easy
    </div>
    
    <div class="terminal-navigation">
      <a href="/" class="terminal-button">RETURN TO MAIN MENU</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</TerminalLayout>

<style>
  .terminal-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .terminal-navigation {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
</style>